[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":134},["Reactive",2],{"frontend_2_10":3,"titleMap":68,"ArticlesSelect_frontend":111},[4,15,25,37,47,57],{"title":5,"description":6,"img":7,"readingTime":8,"createdAt":13,"updatedAt":13,"slug":14},"在Nuxt Content v1中實現程式碼區塊複製貼上功能","用 Nuxt Content 作為部落格的基底讓我最開心的部份，就是 markdown 中的程式碼區塊了，自動上色、格式化、支援的語言非常多，這是很多部落格平台都無法提供的，但若需要程式碼複製貼上功能，就得自己額外處理。","923/YRlYZO.jpg",{"text":9,"minutes":10,"time":11,"words":12},"4 min read",3.32,199200,664,"2023-12-12T05:50:50.000Z","nuxt2_content_code_block_copy_paste",{"title":16,"description":17,"img":18,"readingTime":19,"createdAt":23,"updatedAt":23,"slug":24},"在Nuxt 2中建立動態routes的sitemap","Sitemap 雖然對網站來說非必要，但為了 SEO 考量通常都還是會建立。而在 Nuxt 2 中可以透過@nuxt/sitemap模組來簡單建立 sitemap。但若遇到動態頁面，這個模組無法自動新增，官方文件要求使用者必須自行新增，而官方建議的作法以及網路上查到的方式好像都滿麻煩的，所以自己搞了一個小撇步出來，覺得頗方便，所以就紀錄下來。","923/KaAGJw.png",{"text":9,"minutes":20,"time":21,"words":22},3.37,202200,674,"2023-10-30T09:24:31.000Z","nuxt2_dynamic_routes_sitemap",{"title":26,"description":27,"img":28,"readingTime":29,"createdAt":34,"updatedAt":35,"slug":36},"個人作品集","這篇是整理自己工作中產出或參與的可公開網站，以及自己開發的一些個人專案紀錄。","924/j9gCap.jpg",{"text":30,"minutes":31,"time":32,"words":33},"2 min read",1.935,116100,387,"2023-08-10T06:23:47.000Z","2023-12-11T03:54:57.000Z","collections",{"title":38,"description":39,"img":40,"readingTime":41,"createdAt":45,"updatedAt":35,"slug":46},"解決底部Sticky元素在Android Chrome滾動時渲染位置錯誤的問題","如果不是複雜的需求，對於在元素流中有滾動後要固定的元素，像是頂部 header 滾動後要固定或底部 footer 在滾動前要固定，我都會偏好用position: sticky這個方式去處理，簡單粗暴，不像position: fixed那樣要去計算高度來給其他元素 padding 以防遮住主要內容，或是滾動後要用 JS 去偵測來修改，瀏覽器會幫你做好運算。","922/iRFPQu.jpg",{"text":30,"minutes":42,"time":43,"words":44},1.685,101100,337,"2023-07-14T07:26:50.000Z","mobile_chrome_sticky_bottom",{"title":48,"description":49,"img":50,"readingTime":51,"createdAt":55,"updatedAt":23,"slug":56},"使用nuxt-content-git取得Nuxt2 Content中正確的檔案時間","建完這個部落格之後，發現好像不太對，怎麼前幾天發的文章，日期卻變成今天。後來發現是因為若從 A 電腦更新文章，在 B 電腦用 git 同步更新檔案之後，檔案的更新日期會變成當下的時間。","924/WCeWkF.jpg",{"text":30,"minutes":52,"time":53,"words":54},1.55,93000,310,"2023-01-06T13:35:19.000Z","nuxt2_content_git",{"title":58,"description":59,"img":60,"readingTime":61,"createdAt":65,"updatedAt":66,"slug":67},"Nuxt2中的BootstrapVue TreeShaking","Bootstrap 是個很好用的 UI 框架，在 Vue 生態系中主要由 Bootstrap Vue 去作銜接，然而在專案中幾乎不會完全使用到 Bootstrap 的所有功能，這時如果把不必要的 css / js 編譯移除，可以降低編譯後專案的大小，這種行為也被稱為 Tree shaking。本篇紀錄了自己在 Nuxt2 中使用 Bootstrap Vue 時，Tree Shaking 的一些步驟。","924/Oqxy2g.jpg",{"text":9,"minutes":62,"time":63,"words":64},3.56,213600,712,"2023-01-02T08:03:25.000Z","2023-12-11T10:19:13.000Z","nuxt2_bootstrapvue_treeshaking",{"buy_me_a_tea":69,"canned_fish_dha_epa":70,"collections":26,"crypto_after_ftx":71,"crypto_liquidity_mining_v2":72,"fedora_disable_turbo_boost":73,"fedora_docker_startup":74,"fedora_lineageos_sargo":75,"fedora_megasync":76,"fedora_startup":77,"fedora_unrar":78,"fedora_youtube_download":79,"fedora_zram_resize":80,"free_diving_seeing_friend_black_out_first_time":81,"linux_ten_years_experience":82,"macbook_air_2013_fedora":83,"mark_forster":84,"mobile_chrome_sticky_bottom":38,"nuxt2_bootstrapvue_treeshaking":58,"nuxt2_content_code_block_copy_paste":5,"nuxt2_content_git":48,"nuxt2_dynamic_routes_sitemap":16,"okinawa_first_day_2023":85,"okinawa_foods_2023":86,"okinawa_fourth_day_2023":87,"okinawa_hotel_2023":88,"okinawa_one_day_tour_bus_2023_south":89,"okinawa_one_day_tour_bus_2023":90,"online_survey_money":91,"pixel3a_custom_rom":92,"ubuntu_lineageos_sargo":93,"ubuntu_swap_resize":94,"what_we_know_rainbow_parent":95,"what_we_know_rainbow_therapy":96,"woeusb":97,"chrome_os_flex_asus_e203na":98,"compare_blog":99,"crypto_liquidity_mining_v3":100,"nuxt2_to_nuxt3_blog_0_intro":101,"nuxt2_to_nuxt3_blog_1_ui":102,"nuxt2_to_nuxt3_blog_2_settings":103,"nuxt2_to_nuxt3_blog_3_modules_content":104,"nuxt2_to_nuxt3_blog_4_modules_pwa":105,"nuxt2_to_nuxt3_blog_5_modules_sitemap":106,"nuxt2_to_nuxt3_blog_6_modules_pinia":107,"nuxt3_vite_pwa":108,"vue_stack_deployment_pm2":109,"vue_stack_development_devcontainer":110